<chapter id="chap-Reference_Guide-Configuration">
   <title>Configuration</title>
   <abstract>
    <para>This chapter provides you the basic knowledge about configurations in &PRODUCT; via two main topics: </para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para><link linkend="sect-Reference_Guide-Database_Configuration">Database Configuration</link></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><link linkend="sect-Reference_Guide-EMail_Service_Configuration">Email Service Configuration</link></para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <para>With this knowledge, you can extend more functions for your product and customize to your desires.</para>
    <para>All the configuration discussed in this chapter will be done by editing the main system configuration file <filename>configuration.properties</filename>. This file is located at:</para>
     <table frame='all'>
        <tgroup cols='2' align='left' colsep='1' rowsep='1'>
            <thead>
                <row>
                    <entry>Tomcat</entry>
                    <entry>JBoss</entry>
                </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                <row>
                     <entry><filename>$TOMCAT_HOME/gatein/conf/configuration.properties</filename></entry>
                     <entry><filename>$JBOSS_HOME/server/default/conf/gatein/configuration.properties</filename></entry>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
        </table>
    </abstract>
